libpaseto
------------------------------------------
libpaseto is a low-level implementation of Platform-Agnostic Security Tokens
in C. It only supports v2 public and private tokens, v1 is not supported.
PASETO Registered Claims are not in the scope of this project but can be built
ontop of libpaseto.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.7-1
  libpaseto-devel-1.0-1bl2
  libpaseto1-1.0-1bl2
  libsodium-devel-1.0.20-1
  libsodium26-1.0.20-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  libsodium-devel-1.0.20-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/authenticvision/libpaseto

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/authenticvision/libpaseto/archive/refs/tags/1.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libpaseto-1.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libpaseto-1.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libpaseto-1.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libpaseto-1.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libpaseto1-1.0-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libpaseto-devel-1.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libpaseto)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libpaseto.README
  /usr/share/doc/libpaseto/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/libpaseto/README.md

(libpaseto1)
  /usr/bin/cygpaseto-1.dll

(libpaseto-devel)
  /usr/include/paseto.h
  /usr/lib/libpaseto.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/paseto.pc

